author: Epic Games
description:
People of Note is coming to Epic Games Store in 2026! Wishlist now: https://epic.gm/people-of-note

Cadence is played by two actors: Heather Gonzalez alongside the pop-star vocals of LEXXE. 

About People of Note: In this turn-based RPG musical, join Cadence as she recruits an ensemble of musicians on her quest for stardom. Experience turn-based combat like never before, where each battle is a musical performance with evolving combat conditions and genre-bending mashup attacks!

author: Epic Games
description:
Face your past to shape the future in our latest major update. https://epic.gm/warframepdp

The ancient battlefields of Tau await in our most ambitious update yet! Available now on all platforms, The Old Peace takes your Warframe journey to a whole new level, bringing you face to face with the Orokin and Sentients through memories of The Old War — a galaxy-spanning conflict that until now only existed in whispers and echoes across Warframe's ever-sprawling lore.   

In addition to the latest chapter of our ongoing cinematic Quest, we've made numerous additions to Warframe's cast of characters, innovative game modes for you to dive into, expansions to existing systems, awesome new weaponry and more. And with new upcoming events arriving shortly after launch, there's plenty to keep you busy over the holidays and beyond.   

Best of all, The Old Peace lays key groundwork for an even more expansive, Tau-focused update to come later in 2026. Jump in-game today and experience Warframe like
